settings.description: Demake of the first level of the fangame smbddx

Welcome to a world where yellow thing-a-majigs reign supreme, giants and petites live in harmony, and corals roam across the night sky. It makes absolutely no sense. 
04/26/22 -- 7:53 A.M.

Super Mario Advance 4 but it's a coin hunt.
Find all the 3 Ace-Coins and the 1 E-Coin
You need to recollect 52 coins, touch the object will give you a coin challenge that you need to collect 52 coins in this level, once you end will give you 3up

Goomba's shoes? Venus flytraps spewing up spiky balls? Nipper plants breathing fire? What is this, some sort of Mario game? 

Prod. Code - 103A/104A/106A - 6/22/22, Wed-11:45 am
This level has 5 ace coins and it has 250 sseconds, you need to defeat ludwig to end the level.
Fun Fact: I'm terrible at making underwater levels, so I just decided to take out the water in the underwater, thus creating an... under level.
